<a name="l00689"></a>00689 <span class="comment">   * detection using the libpci backend. Only the common PCI devices (GPUs,</span>
<a name="l00690"></a>00690 <span class="comment">   * NICs, block devices, ...) and host bridges (objects that connect the host</span>
<a name="l00691"></a>00691 <span class="comment">   * objects to an I/O subsystem) will be added to the topology.</span>
<a name="l00692"></a>00692 <span class="comment">   * Uncommon devices and other bridges (such as PCI-to-PCI bridges) will be</span>
<a name="l00693"></a>00693 <span class="comment">   * ignored.</span>
<a name="l00694"></a>00694 <span class="comment">   */</span>
